ZH: 健身对于身体健康非常重要。
EN: Exercising is very important for physical health.

ZH: 我每天早上都会去健身房锻炼。
EN: I go to the gym to exercise every morning.

ZH: 她每个周末都会跑步健身。
EN: She goes running to keep fit every weekend.

ZH: 我们可以一起去健身俱乐部。
EN: We can go to the fitness club together.

ZH: 我计划每周健身三次。
EN: I plan to exercise three times a week.

ZH: 健身不只是为了减肥，还可以增强身体素质。
EN: Exercising is not just for losing weight, it also improves physical fitness.

ZH: 健身可以帮助减轻压力。
EN: Exercising can help reduce stress.

ZH: 吃得健康加上健身可以更好地保持身体健康。
EN: Eating healthy along with exercising can better maintain physical health.

ZH: 我正在学习不同的健身技巧。
EN: I am learning different exercise techniques.

ZH: 我让朋友们加入我的健身团队。
EN: I invited my friends to join my fitness team.

ZH: 他健身的目的是为了参加比赛。
EN: He exercises to participate in competitions.

ZH: 有些人每天早上都会进行跳绳健身。
EN: Some people skip rope for exercise every morning.

ZH: 她最近开始了瑜伽健身。
EN: She has recently started yoga for exercise.

ZH: 运动员们每天都进行专业的健身训练。
EN: Athletes undergo professional fitness training every day.

ZH: 我们家附近有一个很好的健身中心。
EN: There is a good fitness center near our house.

ZH: 健身不仅锻炼身体，也锻炼意志。
EN: Exercising not only exercises the body, but also the willpower.

ZH: 他通过健身锻炼获得了更好的体力。
EN: He has improved his stamina through fitness training.

ZH: 我觉得健身后感觉很轻松。
EN: I feel relaxed after exercising.

ZH: 健身可以帮助改善睡眠质量。
EN: Exercising can help improve sleep quality.

ZH: 我喜欢早晨在户外健身。
EN: I enjoy outdoor workouts in the morning.
